author: Written by: Kristen Soroe
title: Waggaman man accused in St. Charles Parish fatal stabbing
text:
ST. CHARLES PARISH, LA (WVUE) - St. Charles parish deputies say they arrested a Waggaman man who stabbed a person to death.
Deputies say 25-year-old Rodney Naquin Jr. killed Jassen Robert of Ama last Tuesday.
They booked Naquin with second degree murder, as well as armed robbery and obstruction of justice. He's being held at the Nelson Coleman Correctional Center without bond.
